{
  "page": "Pyramid of Rhazdar",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>pyramid of Rhazdar</b> is the seat of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Rhazdar\" title=\"House of Rhazdar\">House of Rhazdar</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>. The building is yellow and green, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_Lotus\" title=\"Purple Lotus\">Purple Lotus</a> is located among the hovels overshadowed by the <a href=\"/index.php/Pyramid\" title=\"Pyramid\">pyramid</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pyramid_of_Rhazdar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_60\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 60\">Chapter 60</a>, The Spurned Suitor.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404210447\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 133/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8534/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 462/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097